title: King Crimson-The Collectable King Crimson, Vol. 3: Live in Londo
description:
Live recording of King Crimson at the Shepherds Bush Empire in London, their final European show on the THRAK tour, featuring the double trio lineup:

DISC 1:
Introductory Soundscape
Conundrum
Thela Hun Ginjeet
Neurotica
Red
Waiting Man
Dinosaur
Three Of A Perfect Pair
Improv I
VROOOM VROOOM
Sex Sleep Eat Drink Dream
VROOOM
Coda: Marine 475

DISC 2:
Larks' Tongues In Aspic, Pt. II
Frame By Frame
Matte Kudasai
B'Boom
THRAK
21st Century Schizoid Man
Indiscipline
Prism
Elephant Talk


Lineup:
Adrian Belew - vocals, guitar
Robert Fripp - guitar, mellotron
Tony Levin - bass, chapman stick
Trey Gunn - warr guitar
Bill Bruford - drums and percussion
Pat Mastelotto - drums and percussion
